Package com.straxov.city

Class СityFactory

java.lang.Object
com.straxov.city.СityFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
EntityFactory
public class СityFactory extends Object implements EntityFactory
CityFactory is a concrete implementation of the EntityFactory interface. It is responsible for creating instances of Bank, Worker, and Spender for the city simulation.
